    Voice
  </h3>

  <hr>

  <p>
    Intuo's voice is human. It’s familiar, friendly, and straightforward.
    Our priority is explaining our products and helping our users get their
    work done so they can get on with their lives. We want to educate people
    without patronizing or confusing them.
  </p>

  <h4><span class="icon ion-lightbulb"></span> Tips</h4>

  <ul>
    <li>Fun but not silly</li>
    <li>Confident but not cocky</li>
    <li>Smart but not stodgy</li>
    <li>Informal but not sloppy</li>
    <li>Helpful but not overbearing</li>
    <li>Expert but not bossy</li>
    <li>Weird but not inappropriate</li>
  </ul>

