    Success message
  </h3>

  <hr>

  <p class="quote">
    Fine piece of work! You deserve a raise.
  </p>

  <h4><span class="icon ion-lightbulb"></span> Tips</h4>

  <ul>
    <li>Pat these users on the back for getting a course out the door.</li>
    <li>Feel free to be casual.</li>
    <li>They’re probably feeling happy and relieved—use casual language that encourages those feelings.</li>
    <li>Feel free to be funny.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="anchor-container">
    <a href="#be-encouraging" class="anchor"><span class="ion-link"></span></a>
